1. `preferences.saveAccount(newAccount)` - saves to storage and commits
2. `unifiedInboxConfigurator.configureUnifiedInbox()` - checks account count

When `configureUnifiedInbox()` calls `accountManager.getAccounts()`, the newly created account should be returned since it was added to the in-memory list when `newAccount()` was called.

