1. `preferences.newAccount(account.uuid)` - this adds the account to `accountsMap` and `accountsInOrder`
2. Then various properties are set on the account
3. `newAccount.markSetupFinished()` - marks setup as finished
4. `preferences.saveAccount(newAccount)` - saves to disk and notifies listeners
5. `unifiedInboxConfigurator.configureUnifiedInbox()` - checks account count

